                                        | PERMANENTE
                        p(lang="en")
                            strong Because technology and data can’t be the ultimate goal. 
                            span It is just a mean to help people to 
                                strong make their work done 
                                | and get on their lifes.  
                            span 
                                strong NGO's Volunteers
                                | , 
                                strong associations 
                                | or  
                                strong campaigners 
